7c67-46a5-bb37-459c7c91c572"],

Cell["\<\
distances = Table[
  geodesicDistanceDeg[21.88, 96.01, stations[[i, 1]], stations[[i, 2]]],
  {i, Length[stations]}
];
refIdx = First[Ordering[Abs[distances - 55], 1]];\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"d9a06b6a-9a63-4cb6-a9d3-91999f82e299"],

